channel.title: Ranger - X!
channel.description:
DevilCheater's Ranger - X !
The best place to use this script is multi fight areas Arrows and bow wield so script can autocolor ! Set up lines 13 - 47 and decleare players in 50 +
The best place to use this script is stronghold security becouse there are no randoms (atleast i didnt get any)
Features *Picks Up arrows *Runs away when low Hp or when fight take too long *AntiBann *AntiRandoms *MultiPlayer (not tested)
If you are using this script , please give me feedback
